&lt;p&gt;Hugo Book is a clean, content-focused documentation theme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="pros"&gt;Pros&lt;a class="anchor" href="#pros"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clean Design&lt;/strong&gt;: No distracting elements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Markdown Friendly&lt;/strong&gt;: Perfectly supports standard Markdown syntax.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multilingual Support&lt;/strong&gt;: Built-in i18n support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="cons"&gt;Cons&lt;a class="anchor" href="#cons"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Custom styles require overriding SCSS variables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="summary"&gt;Summary&lt;a class="anchor" href="#summary"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is very suitable for technical documentation and personal knowledge bases.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>